29#include <libelf.h>

31#include "_libelf.h"
32
33__RCSID("$NetBSD: elf_getbase.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
34ELFTC_VCSID("Id: elf_getbase.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
35
36off_t
37elf_getbase(Elf *e)
38{
39 if (e == NULL) {
40 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
41 return ((off_t) -1);
42 }
43
44 if (e->e_parent == NULL)
45 return ((off_t) 0);
46
47 return ((off_t) ((uintptr_t) e->e_rawfile -
48 (uintptr_t) e->e_parent->e_rawfile));
49}
